#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:1
msgid "Using WebAssembly"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:3
msgid ""
"VTK-Wasm is a prototype infrastructure that enables the compilation of VTK C+"
"+ code to WebAssembly via Emscripten. This feature is still under active "
"development."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:5
msgid ""
"To learn more about VTK-Wasm and its capabilities, please take a look at the "
"following resources:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:7
msgid "[Homepage for VTK.wasm](https://kitware.github.io/vtk-wasm/)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:9
msgid ""
"[Examples of WebAssembly applications that use VTK for rendering.](https://"
"gitlab.kitware.com/vtk/vtk/-/tree/master/Examples/Emscripten/Cxx)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:11
msgid ""
"[A collection of VTK WebAssembly demos.](https://github.com/Kitware/vtk-wasm-"
"demos)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:13
msgid ""
"[A guide on using the experimental WebGPU feature in VTK-Wasm.](https://"
"discourse.vtk.org/t/guide-how-do-i-use-vtk-wasm-webgpu-experimental-"
"feature/11164)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:15
msgid ""
"[Instructions for building VTK using Emscripten for WebAssembly.](../"
"advanced/build_wasm_emscripten.md)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:17
msgid ""
"[vtk-wasm-sdk](https://gitlab.kitware.com/vtk/vtk-wasm-sdk) for building and "
"publishing the [`kitware/vtk-wasm-sdk`](https://hub.docker.com/r/kitware/vtk-"
"wasm-sdk) docker images."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:19
msgid ""
"[Deep dive into WebAssembly & WebGPU in VTK: presentation from April 28th, "
"2023](https://docs.google.com/presentation/"
"d/1Nl0TVa55616QKCSHP54BoYBvByMKe6lIUl6IFZqSeJo/edit#slide=id.p). This "
"presentation covers topics such as Emscripten, VTK-wasm Docker image, WASM "
"Dev tools, VTK and WebGPU: PolyData Mapper, API inspection with RenderDoc, "
"and performance profiles."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../getting_started/using_webassembly.md:21
msgid ""
"We welcome your feedback and contributions to this project. Feel free to "
"share your experiences, questions, and ideas in the [web/vtk-wasm](https://"
"discourse.vtk.org/c/web/vtk-wasm/12) category of the VTK Discourse forum. "
"Stay tuned for updates and new developments!"
msgstr ""
